high_descs: Turn right, go to the window, and turn left toward the small gray counter.
Take the bread from the small gray counter.
Turn left, go to the brown door, turn left, and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the bread in the refrigerator, close the refrigerator, wait for four seconds, open the refrigerator, take the bread from the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator.
Turn left, go to the sink, turn left, and go to the toaster.
Place the bread on the gray counter near the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread near the toaster.

high_descs: Turn to the right, then the left to find the bread.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the counter.
Carry the bread and turn left, then left again to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside. Shut the door then open it again. Take the bread out and shut the door.
Carry the bread and turn left, then left again to find the toast.er
Place the bread on the counter, to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight to the wall, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the counter, to the right of the stove.
Turn left, go straight to the door, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the loaf of bread in the fridge.
Turn left, go straight, then turn left to approach the counter with the coffee maker.
Put the loaf of bread on the counter, in front of the kettle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on the counter.
